Just food for thoughts... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umelcar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melcar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/14/02 6:59:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1133.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: God and Religion (OT)</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  My name isn't Cheese. Burn in hell, heathen!! <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
