I'd have to disagree with this statement.  There are probably as many religious people (Christians in this area) who are yelling and moaning that the Teacher can't get in front of the class and say &quot;Let us Pray&quot; as there are Non-religious people arguing with them saying We don't WANT to pray in school.<br>
